Build instructions for local build
==================================
* create a SLES12 installation source below /path/to/SLE12/repo
  tip: copy SLE12 DVD

* call kiwi prepare:
  kiwi -p suse-SLE12-JeOS --root /tmp/kiwi-sle12 --ignore-repos \
       --add-repo /path/to/SLE12/repo \
       --add-repotype yast2 \
       --add-repo /usr/share/kiwi/repo/suse-repo/suse-sle12-repo/ \
       --add-repotype rpm-dir

* call kiwi create for DASD device:
  kiwi --create /tmp/kiwi-sle12 --ignore-repos \
     --add-repo /path/to/SLE12/repo \
       --add-repotype yast2 \
       --add-repo /usr/share/kiwi/repo/suse-repo/suse-sle12-repo/ \
       --add-repotype rpm-dir \
     -d /tmp/myimage --type vmx --targetDevice /dev/dasdX

* call kiwi create for virtio device (KVM):
  kiwi --create /tmp/kiwi-sle12 --ignore-repos \
       --add-repo /path/to/SLE12/repo \
       --add-repotype yast2 \
       --add-repo /usr/share/kiwi/repo/suse-repo/suse-sle12-repo/ \
       --add-repotype rpm-dir \
       -d /tmp/myimage --type vmx


Kernel paramters to configure the image:
========================================
busid=0.0.0530
qeth_port=VSWL2
qeth_read=0.0.0800
qeth_write=0.0.0801
qeth_ctrl=0.0.0802
qeth_up=1
